{
  "info": {
    "name": "ServiLink API",
    "_postman_id": "servilink-dbp-2026",
    "description": "CS 2031 Desarrollo Basado en Plataformas — UTEC 2026-1\n\n**Instrucciones:**\n1. Importar en Postman\n2. Ir a la carpeta Auth → Register o Login\n3. El token JWT se guarda automáticamente en la variable {{token}}\n4. Todos los endpoints protegidos lo usan sin configuración adicional\n\n**Usuarios de prueba:**\n- carlos@servilink.pe / password123 (CLIENT)\n- juan.rios@servilink.pe / password123 (PROFESSIONAL)\n- maria.condori@servilink.pe / password123 (PROFESSIONAL)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8081", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "token",   "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [

    {
      "name": "🔐 Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register — CLIENT",
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": [
            "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
            "  const r = pm.response.json();",
            "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', r.token);",
            "  console.log('Token guardado:', r.token.substring(0,30)+'...');",
            "}"
          ], "type": "text/javascript" }}],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","auth","register"] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Carlos Mendoza\",\n  \"email\": \"carlos.nuevo@servilink.pe\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\",\n  \"phone\": \"987654321\",\n  \"role\": \"CLIENT\"\n}" }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Register — PROFESSIONAL",
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": [
            "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
            "  const r = pm.response.json();",
            "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', r.token);",
            "}"
          ], "type": "text/javascript" }}],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","auth","register"] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Ana López\",\n  \"email\": \"ana.lopez@servilink.pe\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\",\n  \"phone\": \"976543210\",\n  \"role\": \"PROFESSIONAL\"\n}" }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login — CLIENT (datos de prueba)",
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": [
            "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
            "  const r = pm.response.json();",
            "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', r.token);",
            "  console.log('✅ Token guardado para:', r.email);",
            "}"
          ], "type": "text/javascript" }}],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","auth","login"] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"carlos@servilink.pe\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}" }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login — PROFESSIONAL (Juan Ríos)",
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": [
            "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
            "  const r = pm.response.json();",
            "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', r.token);",
            "  console.log('✅ Token profesional guardado para:', r.email);",
            "}"
          ], "type": "text/javascript" }}],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","auth","login"] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"juan.rios@servilink.pe\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}" }
          }
        }
      ]
    },

